{"data":[{"date":"09:22 08/07","title":"HLV Croatia l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-len-tieng-thach-thuc-anh-o-ban-ket.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0110T Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nNga v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho NHM m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau 2-2 trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u c\u00e2n n\u00e3o Croatia \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-len-tieng-thach-thuc-anh-o-ban-ket.PNG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nHLV Zlatko Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Croatia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Dalic th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-croatia-421-190640.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Croatia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Dalic v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin.<br />\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zlatko Dalic phat bieu ve tran Dan Mach vs Croatia\" title=\"Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ha-dan-mach-vao-tu-ket-hlv-croatia-noi-gi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zlatko Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cAnh r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Croatia c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\n\u201cTrong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 50-50. Ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung\u00a0 k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1027","checkdouble":"190669"},{"date":"09:33 08/07","title":"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fekir","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nabil Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/liverpool-khong-con-co-hoi-chieu-mo-fekir.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Fekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Lyon. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ghi t\u1edbi 18 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ligue 1, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNabil Fekir r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 trung phong c\u1eafm. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield. Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Fekir, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Liverpool th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-gay-soc-vu-muc-tieu-hang-dau-cua-liverpool-172-190006.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Fekir</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Martial, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lyon kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Fekir cho Liverpool</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Liverpool mua Nabil Fekir th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5p, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Lyon, Jean-Michel Aulas kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nabil Fekir\" title=\"Nabil Fekir\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/liverpool-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-tuyen-phap-len-60-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Nabil Fekir</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Fekir s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Lyon, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Fekir h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Lyon, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cFekir l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi, vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1026","checkdouble":"190670"},{"date":"09:55 08/07","title":"\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca h\u00fat kh\u00e1ch Premier League","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/everton-va-tottenham-muon-mua-mina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho Chelsea c\u1ea3. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Conte.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/7/David-Luiz-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh David Luiz s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Luiz c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m David Luiz</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Porto v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 David Luiz ra \u0111i. N\u1ebfu The Blues nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Napoli-muon-mua-David-Luiz-cua-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin \u0111\u1ed3n Porto mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Benfica v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u1edf\u00a0m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a David Luiz, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 cao \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do r\u1eddi n\u01a1i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1025","checkdouble":"190671"},{"date":"10:15 08/07","title":"Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u0103n sao tr\u1ebb h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. H\u1ecd quy\u1ebft s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 22 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Aston Villa bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Grealish</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18, Aston Villa gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1 play-off, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Middlesbrough \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Fulham song sau c\u00f9ng thua 0-1. Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Premier League khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Birmingham \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Tony Xia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Aston Villa s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n \u0111i c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1edbi tai nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i Premier League, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Jack Grealish.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/liverpool-van-muon-mua-grealish.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Tottenham chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho sao tr\u1ebb 22 tu\u1ed5i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Aston Villa ra gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Grealish. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi l\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua c\u00f9ng Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch 2017/18, Grealish l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Aston Villa. Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh nh\u01b0 Tottenham hay Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Grealish. Ph\u00eda Aston Villa hi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Grealish\" title=\"Jack Grealish\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/9/7/hlv-hodgson-giuc-sao-tre-aston-villa-som-chon-dtqg.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua Jack Grealish</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp v\u1eabn \u00e1n binh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, theo th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Mirror, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng Liverpool b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. H\u1ecd \u00e2m th\u1ea7m theo s\u00e1t Grealish v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua kim ti\u1ec1n v\u1edbi Tottenham.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi chia tay Philippe Coutinho, hi\u1ec7n Liverpool v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 ba Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino, HLV Klopp v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-khong-nen-chieu-mo-forsberg-172-190458.html\">Forsberg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-len-tieng-choc-tuc-man-utd-172-190403.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1024","checkdouble":"190672"},{"date":"10:56 08/07","title":"Sadio Mane n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m Mane</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u01b0a tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/them-mot-doi-bong-muon-giai-cuu-david-luiz-172-189742.html\" target=\"_blank\">Los\u00a0Blancos quan t\u00e2m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mane</span> c\u1ee7a Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Sadio-Mane-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real quan t\u00e2m Mane\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Mane l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Liverpool, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Firmino v\u00e0 Salah h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 8 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1eafc b\u00e9n. Liverpool ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Real hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Liverpool b\u1ecf ra 33 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Mane t\u1eeb Southampton, s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0a ra g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed m\u00e0 h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mane t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp noi ve Mane\" title=\"Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Mane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/28/sadio-mane-noi-gi-khi-duoc-real-madrid-quan-tam.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u00f4ng tin Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf M\u1ef9. Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u1edf Liverpool.\"</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Klopp l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1023","checkdouble":"190673"},{"date":"11:12 08/07","title":"David Luiz l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/5/27/david-luiz-len-tieng-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 David Luiz g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec cho Chelsea c\u1ea3. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Conte.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/7/David-Luiz-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh David Luiz s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Luiz c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-tu-choi-ban-david-luiz-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-172-188530.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m David Luiz</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Porto v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua trung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 David Luiz ra \u0111i. N\u1ebfu The Blues nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"David Luiz ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Napoli-muon-mua-David-Luiz-cua-Chelsea-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Luiz kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i nghe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin \u0111\u1ed3n Porto mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Benfica v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u1edf\u00a0m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a David Luiz, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Chelsea. V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 cao \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u1edf Stamford Bridge, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do r\u1eddi n\u01a1i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1022","checkdouble":"190674"},{"date":"10:44 08/07","title":"HLV Croatia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 k\u00ecm n\u00e9n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Nga \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh. Sau 90 ph\u00fat ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Denis Cheryshev l\u00e0m n\u00ean si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m \u1edf ph\u00fat 31 th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 8 ph\u00fat sau, Andrej Kramaric g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai \u0111\u1ed9i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 v\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y cu\u1ed9c r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp di\u1ec5n. Ph\u00fat 100, Domagoj Vida \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2-1. V\u00e0 khi ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Mario Fernandes l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 cho h\u1ecd 5 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ebft gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Zlatko-Dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Croatia-vs-Nga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nga sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Croatia l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3. H\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Dalic kh\u00f4ng n\u00e9n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. HLV c\u1ee7a Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea5u \u0111i c\u1ea3m x\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m. \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fac m\u1eebng Stanislav Cherchesov (HLV Nga) v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u2026 Nga \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb9p\u201d, Dalic n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Dalic va BHL Croatia\" title=\"Dalic va BHL Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/dalic-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. C\u00e1m \u01a1n c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Nga, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. T\u00f4i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nu\u1ed1t n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb cho\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3p b\u1edfi c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Croatia h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nga tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/croatia-vao-ban-ket-dejan-lovren-khen-dt-nga-465-190657.html\">Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-chien-sieu-kich-tinh-nga-vs-croatia-469-190656.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-ve-tran-dau-voi-nga-465-190655.html\">HLV Zlatko Dalic: Nga vs Croatia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-croatia-465-190653.html\">HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1021","checkdouble":"190675"},{"date":"11:08 08/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 chuy\u1ec7n Croatia b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Croatia c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Croatia kh\u00f4ng lo th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Croatia v\u00e0 Nga tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Olimpiyskiy Fisht \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh t\u1edbi t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Sau 90 ph\u00fat t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u00e0 120 ph\u00fat h\u00f2a 2-2, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3. H\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Anh r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o caro tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn, song \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luka Modric c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luka Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Luka-Modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-Croatia-vs-Nga-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 20 n\u0103m</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d, Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga. \u201cM\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCroatia c\u00f3 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec trong vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y c\u00e1ch Anh v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Croatia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 qua c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Modric kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2 sau 20 n\u0103m\u201d, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 32 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Modric va dong doi Croatia\" title=\"Modric va dong doi Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/luka-modric-phat-bieu-sau-tran-croatia-vs-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Modric ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Nga \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n n\u0103m 1998. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n: M\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh, m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eefa t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 1998 di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Ph\u00e1p, Croatia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. H\u1ecd thua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Croatia vs Nga tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-chien-sieu-kich-tinh-nga-vs-croatia-469-190656.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/croatia-vao-ban-ket-dejan-lovren-khen-dt-nga-465-190657.html\">Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-ve-tran-dau-voi-nga-465-190655.html\">HLV Zlatko Dalic: Nga vs Croatia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-croatia-465-190653.html\">HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1020","checkdouble":"190676"},{"date":"11:26 08/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \"T\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 h\u00e3o huy\u1ec1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/nguoi-hung-tuyen-anh-toi-dang-song-trong-giac-mo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay, trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi v\u1ebb m\u1eb7t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Maguire \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng trong m\u01a1<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Leicester \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ca ng\u1ee3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 xa, n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 3 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Harry Maguire c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00f3p ng\u00f3p v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 Hull City hay Wigan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 EURO 2016, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0\u2026 C\u0110V c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Maguire c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn l\u1edbn khi gia nh\u1eadp Leicester v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2017. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u2013 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong v\u00f2ng 1-2 n\u0103m qua. T\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i \u0111ang s\u1ed1ng trong gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 h\u00e3o huy\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn ra th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh theo th\u1eddi gian. Tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry Maguire chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry Maguire chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/nguoi-hung-tuyen-anh-toi-dang-song-trong-giac-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, Maguire ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh, gi\u00fap \u0110T ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u2013 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mong ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec h\u01a1n th\u1ebf? Nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n r\u1ea5t cao, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u cho \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Dele Alli. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 ch\u00fat l\u01a1 l\u00e0 \u1edf cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 (\u0110T Anh \u0111em c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0)\u201d \u2013 Harry Maguire chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV Gareth Southgate ca ng\u1ee3i Maguire l\u00e0 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3\u201d \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, v\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng anh l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi-421-190658.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi-421-190658.html\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129!</span><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Harry n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ee9u b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Harry kh\u00e1c ra tay. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 10 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/214818-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1019","checkdouble":"190677"},{"date":"11:33 08/07","title":"Rashford kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0 tr\u1ebb con sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/8/rashford-khoc-nhu-tre-con-sau-tran-thang-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcus Rashford kh\u00f3c n\u1ee9c n\u1edf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng k\u00ecm n\u00e9n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau khi Tam s\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-anh-vs-thuy-dien-421-190634.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span> trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, song h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcus Rashford kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0 tr\u1ebb con sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marcus Rashford kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0 tr\u1ebb con sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Marcus-Rashford-khoc-nhu-tre-con-sau-tran-thang-Thuy-Dien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ea7y thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Croatia, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf c\u1eb7p t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft ngay sau \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Anh \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cH\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, Anh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Maguire gi\u00fap Anh d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, Anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rashford kh\u00f3c n\u1ee9c n\u1edf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcus Rashford kh\u00f3c n\u1ee9c n\u1edf sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, ng\u00f4i sao 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng k\u00ecm n\u00e9n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac sau khi Tam s\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rashford khoc nhu mua sau tran thang Thuy Dien\" title=\"Rashford kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0 m\u01b0a sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/rashford-khoc-nhu-tre-con-sau-tran-thang-thuy-dien.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rashford kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0 m\u01b0a sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n \u1edf ph\u00fat 91 thay Raheem Sterling, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u00e2u gi\u1edd nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u vang l\u00ean, Rashford \u0111\u1ed5 g\u1ee5c xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u00f4m m\u1eb7t kh\u00f3c. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1997 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRashford sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn Victor Lindelof, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf M.U \u0111\u1ec3 an \u1ee7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u00f9ng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1018","checkdouble":"190679"},{"date":"07:58 08/07","title":"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup: L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu Harry n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u1ee9u b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Harry kh\u00e1c ra tay. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 10 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Harry Maguire s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng ai ng\u1edd t\u1edbi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n<div style=\"text - align:center; width: 100 %; padding: 20px 0; \"><video class=\"hlsvideoobj\" data-src=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/DRM/HLS/201807/275571/master.m3u8\" controls=\"\"></video></div>\r\nV\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Harry Maguire ch\u00e2n \u01b0\u1edbt ch\u00e2n r\u00e1o gia nh\u1eadp Leicester City sau khi c\u00f9ng Hull City xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gi\u1edd, trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t trong h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV Gareth Southgate thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Quay cu\u1ed3ng ch\u00f3ng m\u1eb7t l\u1eafm kh\u00f4ng Harry, khi anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1m b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n m\u1edbi h\u00f2 h\u1eb9n nhau ra qu\u1ea7y bar c\u1ed5 v\u0169 Tam S\u01b0 \u1edf Euro 2016 qua m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh TV?</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Harry-Maguire-tran-Anh-vs-Thuy-Dien-Nguoi-hung-bat-dac-di-Tam-Su-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire m\u1edbi hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t C\u0110V v\u00f4 danh theo ch\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf Euro 2016</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> V\u1edbi b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Kyle Walker c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi John Stones d\u00e2ng cao l\u00ean khu trung tuy\u1ebfn, Southgate h\u1eb3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1n th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean Gary Cahill v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u1eadn Tunisia ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai tu\u1ea7n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Kh\u00f4ng, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 47 tu\u1ed5i thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Maguire v\u00f4 danh v\u00e0 non n\u1edbt \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u1ec7ch tr\u00e1i, gi\u1eb1ng x\u00e9 d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng lu\u1ed3ng tranh c\u00e3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00f4ng &ndash; d\u0169ng c\u1ea3m, li\u1ec1u l\u0129nh hay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c, r\u1ea5t ngu ng\u1ed1c. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf, canh b\u1ea1c \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Harry Kane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd, v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp m\u1edf ra c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m cho n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup L\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Harry, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang ngh\u0129! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Anh-vao-ban-ket-World-Cup-Lai-la-nguoi-hung-Harry,-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfng vang trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y \u1edf Leicester City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> H\u00ecnh th\u1ec3 h\u1ed9 ph\u00e1p ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 (cao 1m95 v\u00e0 n\u1eb7ng 100kg) khi\u1ebfn Maguire c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 b\u1ecb \u0111eo b\u00e1m, theo k\u00e8m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean ch\u00ednh, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua anh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n hay ho m\u00e0 k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e3nh di\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Tunisia, Panama r\u1ed3i Colombia, ba \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ba n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1c nhau, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 sau c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn ch\u1ecbu ph\u1eadn n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a 7/9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\" target=\"_blank\">g\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh ph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh &quot;\u0102ng-l\u00ea&quot; Harry Kane</span>, Maguire v\u00e0 Stones sau khi x\u1edbi tung nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 l\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-ra-quan-suon-se-niem-hy-vong-tu-2-chang-harry-421-188889.html\">\u0110T Anh ra qu\u00e2n su\u00f4n s\u1ebb: Ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb hai ch\u00e0ng Harry</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">7 l\u00ean 8 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Maguire d\u00e1n m\u1eaft v\u00e0o tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng bay t\u1eeb ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ashley Young \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i phi th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t t\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00fang \u0111i\u1ec3m giao c\u1eaft, cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u00e1o v\u00e0ng qu\u1ea7n xanh n\u00e0o, hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 full \u0111\u1ecf, n\u1eb1m \u0111o s\u00e0n n\u1ebfu d\u00e1m c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng lao m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c t\u00e0n ph\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ong \u0111\u1ebfm c\u1ee7a anh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">M\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh th\u1eb3ng b\u0103ng, Anh 1-0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, ph\u00fat 30, t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Anh vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/lot-vao-ban-ket-nguoi-anh-bat-dau-mo-cup-vang.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n m\u1edf ra c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m cho Tam S\u01b0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em><span style=\"color:#111111\"> &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00e1t khao v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i.&rdquo;</span></em><span style=\"color:#111111\"> &ndash; Chia s\u1ebb ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a Maguire sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11, v\u1ec1 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 tr\u1ebb trung \u0111ang dung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng anh trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. C\u0169ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Maguire gia nh\u1eadp Leicester v\u1edbi c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 12-17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 r\u1ebb \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00edt ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m, g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 v\u00f4 danh, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ebfm hoi ch\u01a1i tr\u1ecdn 38 tr\u1eadn Premier League cho B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf King Power.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cau-chuyen-ve-harry-maguire-nguoi-hung-nhu-buoc-ra-tu-tro-choi-gia-lap-465-190649.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/cau-chuyen-ve-harry-maguire-nguoi-hung-nhu-buoc-ra-tu-tro-choi-gia-lap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cau-chuyen-ve-harry-maguire-nguoi-hung-nhu-buoc-ra-tu-tro-choi-gia-lap-465-190649.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra t\u1eeb tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i gi\u1ea3 l\u1eadp</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Harry Maguire t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng hai Anh \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eadp tr\u00ecnh trong tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed v\u1eady.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">V\u1eady m\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e0ng ho\u00e0ng m\u00e0 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00f3 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 kho\u1ea3ng hai th\u00e1ng, Maguire ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 trong chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn London v\u00e0 ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi n\u0103m b\u00e0n thua tr\u1eafng l\u00e0m qu\u00e0 t\u1eeb Crystal Palace.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-anh-vs-thuy-dien-421-190634.html\" target=\"_blank\">Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span> bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i d\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u01a1n khi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 co c\u1ee5m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n b\u1edfi Maguire, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gieo r\u1eafc \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng cho Marcus Berg t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Maguire, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i anh v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t &ndash; s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng hay tinh th\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Harry Maguire tran Anh vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"Harry Maguire tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/anh-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-lai-la-nguoi-hung-harry-nhung-khong-phai-nhu-ban-dang-nghi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1, ch\u1ee9ng minh cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\"> Nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea5p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf lu\u00f4n tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00fang ki\u1ec3u &ldquo;kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u chui l\u00ean&rdquo; nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c n\u00e0o trong n\u0103m nay c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n c\u00e1i v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh b\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Maguire. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t k\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i cu\u1ed9c so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Tam S\u01b0, gi\u1edd trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp to\u00e0n h\u00f2a v\u00e0 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup, \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 28 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Italia 90 &ndash; m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eafc ghi c\u00f4ng danh cho Harry Maguire.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#111111\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean r\u1ed3i, trung v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Leicester s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 trong v\u00f2ng h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2><strong>D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</strong><strong><br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0, \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1017","checkdouble":"190658"},{"date":"07:34 08/07","title":"B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng, Suarez h\u1eb1n h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/bi-loai-cay-dang-suarez-han-hoc-to-griezmann-dao-duc-gia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luis Suarez nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u00ecnh y\u00eau c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-0 Uruguay khi\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao Barcelona tan m\u1ed9ng World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/du-am-uruguay-vs-phap-02-sai-lam-nhung-khoanh-khac-va-giot-nuoc-mat-nghen-ngao-421-190576.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span> \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, v\u1edbi hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Raphael Varane v\u00e0 Antoine Griezmann. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9, ng\u00f4i sao Atletico Madrid ch\u1ec9 l\u1eb3ng l\u1eb7ng quay v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7u nh\u1ea3y h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y.</span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Suarez t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luis Suarez t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/bi-loai-cay-dang-suarez-han-hoc-to-griezmann-dao-duc-gia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Luis Suarez t\u1ed1 Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-0 Uruguay t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">M\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00fd do xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t may m\u1eafn khi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Fernando Muslera m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1eaft d\u00ednh b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eb1ng sau nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Griezmann quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 anh m\u1edbi gi\u00e3i b\u00e0y:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 vui v\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh World Cup. Th\u1ef1c ra, t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i bu\u1ed3n h\u01a1n v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Atleti c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn (Diego Godin v\u00e0 Jose Gimenez). T\u00f4i v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 v\u0103n h\u00f3a Uruguay, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u1ea3m x\u00fac khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u201cB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u0169ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.\u201d - Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Griezmann th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-griezmann-truoc-tran-phap-vs-uruguay-421-190375.html\" target=\"_blank\">\"m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay\u201d</span>, coi \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Nam M\u1ef9 nh\u01b0 qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Griezmann ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec c\u00e1i t\u00e1t v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t Luis Suarez. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 2-0 Uruguay \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Barcelona th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1eb1n h\u1ecdc \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ecf v\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3, n\u00f3i:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">\u201cGriezmann kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111\u00e2u. C\u1eadu ta l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n lo\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e2u c\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3cth\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ed1 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay nh\u01b0ng xin l\u1ed7i, ch\u00fang ta r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c nhau.\u201d<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-quet-sach-nam-my-thien-bien-van-hoa-voi-hai-bo-mat-421-190609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/phap-quet-sach-nam-my-thien-bien-van-hoa-voi-hai-bo-mat.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/phap-quet-sach-nam-my-thien-bien-van-hoa-voi-hai-bo-mat-421-190609.html\">Ph\u00e1p qu\u00e9t s\u1ea1ch Nam M\u1ef9: Thi\u00ean bi\u1ebfn v\u1ea1n h\u00f3a v\u1edbi hai b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t</span><br>\r\nPeru, Argentina v\u00e0 n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n Uruguay m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ee9 hai trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1016","checkdouble":"190662"},{"date":"07:36 08/07","title":"B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: Man Utd \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh m\u00e0 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 \u0111ang th\u1eafng l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n 50 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111ang thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 \u1edf Premier League.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh th\u1eafng th\u1ebf<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 92 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Premier League (chi\u1ebfm t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 44.56%). Con s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Anh vs Thuy Dien\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/ban-ket-world-cup-2018-man-utd-dung-thu-hai-ve-so-cau-thu-gop-mat.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Anh l\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p (Ligue 1) v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (La Liga) v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. C\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c, Italia (7), B\u1ec9, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Croatia (2), Scotland, \u00c1o, Nga, Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0 Ukraine (1).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc (Ligue 1 - t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 39.1%) v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh, chi\u1ebfm 21.7%. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f2n th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 12 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Anh. Croatia c\u00f3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i Anh l\u00e0 Dejan Lovren (Liverpool).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tottenham nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 41 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi c\u00e1c CLB \u1edf Premier League s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y nh\u1ea5t. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00e0 Tottenham v\u1edbi 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ed3m Harry Kane, Dele Alli, Eric Dier, Trippier, Danny Rose (Anh), Alderweireld, Vertonghen, Mousa Dembele (B\u1ec9), Hugo Lloris (Ph\u00e1p).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBa \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng sau l\u00e0 Chelsea, Man Utd v\u00e0 Man City v\u1edbi c\u00f9ng 7 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p l\u00e0 Liverpool (4), Leicester (2), Arsenal, Everton, Burnley, Stoke v\u00e0 West Brom (1).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o khung 1h00 v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 (11/7) v\u00e0 Croatia vs Anh (12/7).<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/croatia-vao-ban-ket-dejan-lovren-khen-dt-nga-465-190657.html\">Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien-465-190650.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-tuyen-anh-di-len-tu-tuyet-vong-thanh-tuyet-voi-421-190648.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111i l\u00ean t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lot-vao-ban-ket-nguoi-anh-bat-dau-mo-cup-vang-421-190647.html\">L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ng\u