e=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">08/07 17:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Daegu - FC Seoul</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">08/07 17:30</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Sangju Sangmu - Ulsan Hyundai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1014","checkdouble":"190665"},{"date":"08:14 08/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/8/lich-thi-dau-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 qua \u0111i v\u00e0 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n. L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd  di\u1ec5n ra trong hai ng\u00e0y 11/7 v\u00e0 12/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u1ede c\u1eb7p t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn B\u1ec9. Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Sau khi trung v\u1ec7 Varane \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 40, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u do th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. Pha ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Fernandinho v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Roberto Martinez v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, l\u1ecbch b\u00e1n k\u1ebft WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, l\u1ecbch b\u00e1n k\u1ebft WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/phap-bi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1i qua, hai pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Maguire v\u00e0 Dele Alli gi\u00fap tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch 4 \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 28 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao cho Croatia sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Balkan v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang c\u00e2n n\u00e3o. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nhau 2-2 trong 120 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf c\u1eb7p b\u00e1n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 11/7, tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Saint Petersburg. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Anh s\u1ebd tranh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 chung k\u1ebft c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0o l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7 (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Luzhniki.<br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ecaCH THI \u0110\u1ea4U B\u00c1N K\u1ebeT WORLD CUP 2018</h2>\r\n- 01:00 ng\u00e0y 11/7: Ph\u00e1p vs B\u1ec9<br>\r\n- 01:00 ng\u00e0y 12/7: Anh vs Croatia<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1013","checkdouble":"190666"}]}